Vectors are animals that are capable of carrying
disease pathogens from a reservoir, an animal,

2
00:00:10,850 --> 00:00:14,760
a human or an environment to another host.

3
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:19,910
They are a major cause of sickness and death
in many humanitarian contexts.

4
00:00:19,910 --> 00:00:28,930
In addition to transmitting diseases, some
vector may also be considered as a nuisance

5
00:00:28,930 --> 00:00:36,579
because of the painful bite or due to the
